00:01:47.936 --> 00:01:49.796 A:middle
something that works well with

00:01:49.796 --> 00:01:51.416 A:middle
each component deeply

00:01:51.416 --> 00:01:53.046 A:middle
considered, and each aspect

00:01:53.356 --> 00:01:55.326 A:middle
carefully crafted -- that that

00:01:55.326 --> 00:01:56.986 A:middle
can be profoundly beautiful.

