00:03:15.136 --> 00:03:16.636 A:middle
internally coherent.

00:03:17.136 --> 00:03:19.876 A:middle
On the technology front, we're

00:03:19.876 --> 00:03:22.486 A:middle
evaluating technology usage, and

00:03:22.486 --> 00:03:23.636 A:middle
so we're looking for apps that

00:03:23.636 --> 00:03:25.096 A:middle
