00:03:28.946 --> 00:03:30.186 A:middle
capabilities of our latest

00:03:30.216 --> 00:03:32.506 A:middle
devices, and we're looking for

00:03:32.506 --> 00:03:34.926 A:middle
apps that use the latest Apple

00:03:34.926 --> 00:03:37.686 A:middle
technologies to do really great

00:03:37.736 --> 00:03:38.466 A:middle
new things.

00:03:39.166 --> 00:03:41.836 A:middle
And on the innovation front,

00:03:42.656 --> 00:03:44.216 A:middle
we're looking for brilliance.

00:03:45.076 --> 00:03:47.306 A:middle
We're looking for new ideas.

00:03:48.186 --> 00:03:50.296 A:middle
We're looking for uniqueness,

00:03:51.556 --> 00:03:54.476 A:middle
platform differentiation, and

00:03:54.546 --> 00:03:55.606 A:middle
things that just weren't

00:03:55.606 --> 00:03:56.666 A:middle
possible before.

