00:04:22.926 --> 00:04:24.886 A:middle
dedication that goes into the

00:04:24.936 --> 00:04:26.006 A:middle
pursuit of excellence.

00:04:26.736 --> 00:04:29.706 A:middle
We want to recognize the

00:04:29.806 --> 00:04:32.196 A:middle
dead-ends, and the frustration,

00:04:32.476 --> 00:04:34.196 A:middle
and the exhaustion sometimes

00:04:34.676 --> 00:04:37.626 A:middle
that often goes unseen, and

00:04:37.626 --> 00:04:38.786 A:middle
we're all familiar with that.

00:04:39.956 --> 00:04:41.066 A:middle
And we want to honor the

00:04:41.066 --> 00:04:43.086 A:middle
unconventional thinking, the

00:04:43.086 --> 00:04:45.756 A:middle
creativity, and the new ideas

00:04:46.066 --> 00:04:48.176 A:middle
that lead to breakthroughs and

00:04:48.176 --> 00:04:49.496 A:middle
innovative solutions.

